uc3m.bomberman.entity

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • uc3m.bomberman.entity.Entity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bomb, MovableEntity

    public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents an entity in the game, with and id and a position. Entities do not necessarily move.
    See Also:
    {@link MovableEntity}

        path - Sprite path
        maxHp - Maximum health
        position - Initial position of the Entity
